<item>
            <title>[LU-13056] lctl llog_catlist, llog_print, etc. should default to MGS device</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13056</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The &quot;&lt;tt&gt;lctl llog_print&lt;/tt&gt;&quot;, &quot;&lt;tt&gt;lctl llog_catlist&lt;/tt&gt;&quot;, and related commands should default to using the &quot;MGS&quot; device if it is not specified.  This is overwhelmingly the most common device to use (it isn&apos;t clear that the work for any other device), and having to add &quot;&lt;tt&gt;--device MGS&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; for each use just adds usage difficulty without any benefit.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
